Class MathCalculations

  • java.lang.Object
    • MathCalculations
  • public class MathCalculations
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class has two methods that find the Max and Min values of three numbers that are entered as parameters to each method. The Min method accepts three integers, and the Max method accepts three doubles. It then outputs the Min and Max of the entered values that are specified in the program. The Min method has an int return value and the Max method has a double return value.
